OL,3,CBrittany Ferries set to become
OL,4,Cmajority owner of Condor
OL,6,FBrittany Ferries are set to become the
OL,7,Fmajority owner of Condor Ferries which
OL,8,Fprovides a number of freight and
OL,9,Fpassenger services between the UK, the
OL,10,FChannel Islands and France.
OL,12,FCondor was bought by a consortium
OL,13,Fincluding Brittany Ferries and the
OL,14,FLondon-based Columbia Threadneedle
OL,15,FEuropean Sustainable Infrastructure
OL,16,FFund in November 2019.
