OL,3,CBrittany Ferries set to become
OL,4,Cmajority owner of Condor
OL,6,FIf approved by regulators in Jersey
OL,7,Fand Guernsey over the next few weeks,
OL,8,Fthe latest move would see Brittany
OL,9,FFerries own a controlling 51% stake of
OL,10,FCondor - Columbia Threadneedle would
OL,11,Fkeep a minority shareholding.
OL,13,FBrittany Ferries will support Condor's
OL,14,Fbid to continue supplying Channel
OL,15,FIslands' freight and passenger
OL,16,Fservices as its current contract is
OL,17,Fdue to expire in March 2025.
OL,19,FThe routes are up for tender with
OL,20,Frival operator DFDS also in the
OL,21,Frunning.
