OL,3,CBrittany Ferries set to become
OL,4,Cmajority owner of Condor
OL,6,FBrittany Ferries' Chief Executive
OL,7,FChristophe Mathieu told ITV News in
OL,8,FMarch that there would be a closer
OL,9,Fworking relationship between the two
OL,10,Fcompanies after he replaced Condor
OL,11,Fboss John Napton as the ferry
OL,12,Foperator's interim head.
OL,14,FIn a new statement, Mr Mathieu adds:
OL,15,F"Brittany Ferries has the experience,
OL,16,Fexpertise and scale, along with
OL,17,Fextensive knowledge of the transport
OL,18,Fsector and customer service to
OL,19,Fimplement best practices, which
OL,20,Fultimately will result in a better
OL,21,Fservice for Condor's passengers.
