OL,3,CBrittany Ferries set to become
OL,4,Cmajority owner of Condor
OL,6,F"This change demonstrates our
OL,7,Fcommitment to the Channel Islands,
OL,8,Fshows Brittany Ferries is adding
OL,9,Fstrength and depth to the existing
OL,10,Fteam and delivers community and
OL,11,Fresilience in the long term.
OL,13,F"We believe we operate exactly the
OL,14,Fright fleet for the islands: a mix of
OL,15,Fconventional freight and passenger
OL,16,Fferries for lifeline freight and
OL,17,Ftravel for islanders, alongside the
OL,18,Fhigh speed vessels that are essential
OL,19,Ffor supporting the visitor economies
OL,20,Fof Jersey and Guernsey."
